ish"},{"pid":"760265c889447a3c164b9288d38592067ddd99c2","tid":1616051,"uid":20448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:32:25.000Z","msg":"人就到左 <br />\n等緊手足<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FSH66rZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFSH66rZ.png&h=acf6ed4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc008c9ccdde9e0ce0089d508d6c0dfef8624a09","tid":1616051,"uid":302165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5a4eae99d5993c34fad132935287703dce18d27","tid":1616051,"uid":310883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:29:59.000Z","msg":"紅土區既人已經沈默左好耐 上次8.17光復完後都冇一星期啲旅行團又再侵佔呢區 加上今晚九區集結冇個近紅土 所以以家紅土人都有個集結地<br />\n<br />\n紅磡;土瓜灣;何文田人聯誼地<br />\n日期：3/10<br />\n時間：1945<br />\n地點：黃埔M&amp;S對出/黃埔A出口<br />\n建議活動：唱榮光，文宣 ，口號，最緊要聚左人先，參考昨日中環<br />\n請帶備memo字，原子筆等等<br />\n歡迎各位街坊到場交流自己對紅土區的熱愛之情 今晚八點不見不散<br />\n係紅土黃何既人就同我推爆佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n九區集結樓主幫手開新post加埋上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XDQaPUz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXDQaPUz.jpg&h=79a491ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:32:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">要做ON九秀才，咁就咪革命<br />\n<br />\n依家焗住，打場不對稱戰爭<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Asymmetric_warfare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FAsymmetric_warfare&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEv5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=e70d5c57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Asymmetric_warfare</a><br />\n<br />\n不要硬碰硬<br />\n<br />\n毛澤東：敵進我退，打游擊戰<br />\n<br />\n破壞敵方資源為主！對方在明，我方在暗！<br />\n<br />\n打擊藍絲陣營設備及落單人仕，包括紅色機構，商店，落單瘋狗及奴才、契弟、契女！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盡量組職可靠手足，成立特別小蹤隊！<br />\n<br />\n每小蹤隊10人左右出擊，後勤10人支援放哨補給！<br />\n<br />\n只要有100小蹤隊，特區鷹犬死都唔惦！<br />\n<br />\n不過，慎防敵方埋伏、卧底、䧟阱！</span></span>"},{"pid":"2758ccac11b730ae851807f19e9b460336443a38","tid":1616051,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:32:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76967f57b62bfb146edaf66d8e1377ba37e3aa2d","tid":1616051,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:32:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2849037ea0ab0ee447a1888aafa9886eb0f80cfb","tid":1616051,"uid":266672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86145f40672da28b7c9dde6af435340470c441df","tid":1616051,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:33:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />pish"},{"pid":"6709e60bbe42e768660b9609fbdb973e76199df9","tid":1616051,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:35:00.000Z","msg":"黃埔要人！屌左個保安全日既街坊去左邊啊？？？"},{"pid":"03bab27c23bcaefee48f524b9cfbcdb9156d01f5","tid":1616051,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />pish"},{"pid":"46528692ec4be0e941d01831982194e05eb20334","tid":1616051,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agre